snippet.title: Best VGM 1834 - Soul Calibur - The New Legend (Kilik & Edge's Theme)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast / Arcade / XBLA
Soul Calibur (1999)
The New Legend (Kilik & Edge's Theme)
Junichi Nakatsuru
